Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经不能再在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前的那个时候一样  大家一起来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和大家都等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个人聚在一起的话  一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:09.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(45,270)}「再见的意义」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  跟汐音发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天还以为已经和好如初了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经说了要和我一起做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又想不开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说些什么呢  汐音只是很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里面是很想在一起的  只是害羞不敢说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  不要乱说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是直接去问过的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你是喜欢还是讨厌乃乃香  说清楚啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真能问得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那还用说吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以乃乃香  期待着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我相信汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没有跟乃乃香她们在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  我有件事情想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望实现之后  飞碟会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望实现之后  又会被新的愿望召唤而去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟被大家召唤过来的时候是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「飞碟  飞碟」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拜托你  实现我的愿望吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就可以实现乃乃香和汐音的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  就回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星象仪  诺艾尔也会去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  给我入场券吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是飞碟没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系啦  所以诺艾尔也要去看星象仪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  汐音也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样大家都会笑开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭  周日我大概会去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有点迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有三天  必须赶快做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小春哭着说「这样子一定赶不上了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是为了馒头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实也是人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不早说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西四个人怎么做的来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该就能赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你也来干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不发出指示的话  大家怎么知道自己要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  就算没有你的指示  大家也能好好干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快去动手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊  一副自以为是的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  汐音的话一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她和大家一样  也给了诺艾尔入场券
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以汐音也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要让它成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发生让爸爸担心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是希望尽快去你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  明明是自己说要留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊  真是一转眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然啊  不会有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家聚在一起  又像过去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小春的馒头庆祝圆满成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不关好门  全都看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太  过来  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(528,168,528,-10)\1c000000\bord0\frz-9}星象仪展示中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(148,75,148,-103)\1c000000\bord0\frz5.8}这里是星象仪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到柚季的兴趣也有发挥作用的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在一起的话  这么多才够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书上写的东西  谁也没有认真听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音相信的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不止我们两个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人悄悄在商量什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要拜托大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来召唤飞碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟啊  真的来了的话真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定会吓一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会上电视呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  柚季  凑太都笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音也会变得开心起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是大家的愿望
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单过头了吧  有点无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个必须的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤飞碟的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要怀着某种愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就能引发很强的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  许愿就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说飞碟会帮助我们实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是愿望有很多很多的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选其中一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥这个吝啬鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为许下的愿望要是跟别人说了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能实现不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟  飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的真是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她约好在这里等的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香带诺艾尔去逛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的工作就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到汐音的话  就立刻联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会拿着这个在校舍里绕绕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻起来好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(332,33)\1c000000\bord0\frz-21\fs20}年糕小豆汤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是甜的  吃起来暖洋洋的  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  乃乃香  汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是去了星象仪那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完后  我们先回去柚季那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星象仪在这边的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭才刚刚开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宫也在吗  来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我向老师打听了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川今天缺席了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔你在这里等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟汐音家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道地址吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香她们回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去看看星象仪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和大家一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过一会大家就会来齐的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  跑得太快了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  谁叫你带着这玩意去追她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川的住址  我用邮件发给她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我应该往哪边走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才看见她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本想告诉你不要接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去北美祭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我没讲清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不想和你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为不原谅我所以才不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你等了七年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不能让你马上会原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我对汐音你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗  我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听到你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再对我说无谓的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔也在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把票送给她  其实是想和她一起看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家  和诺艾尔一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看星象仪  一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和过去一样  和大家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起聊天  一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一副亲昵的模样  叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再称呼你「户川同学」了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看到你  不想再听到你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想和你成为什么好友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能再笑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  诺艾尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会做出无法兑现的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会让他人去期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  古宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香找到汐音了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  五人不聚在一起的话  不就没意义了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过来帮忙收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  收拾的活就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾的话就交给我们处理就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特意让你们过来了  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不可以放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  诺艾尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才明明还在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追乃乃香了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去找一下她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
